text: Not sure if it’s a new store, because I usually use Deliveroo to order food. The taste of the Sichuan Pickles Chicken Pot is really good, it’s my top choice so far. I also tried the Braised Fish Fillet Pot and the Sweet and Sour Tofu. All the dishes have a rich, bold flavor, and I’m really satisfied with the taste. I’ll definitely order again. The prices are also reasonable compared to most others.
Likes the classic chicken braised pot, plenty of chicken pieces, worththe price. Better option than Cai Fan

Mala Braised Pot is super good, the Garlic Braised Pot is so special, my kids love it.

Will visit again to try other dishes, cos too many good food to try.
